description.displayText: Brianna has babysat for my 3 children on occasion for the past 4 years. She is very responsible and trustworthy. Brianna is outgoing and my children love her warm and nurturing ways. She is very engaging and my children have a lot of fun with her. Brianna would be an asset to any family she worked for.

description.displayText: Brianna was recommended to me through a friend.  She is an amazing babysitter. I have a 6 year old boy and he adores her.  She interacts with my son so well.  She loves playing sports with him or just relaxing and reading books.  If I had to describe Brianna in two words they would be trust and dependability.
